          "process_md": "##### ***Registration Process***\n\n- Visit the Gujarat Tribal Development Corporation [official website](https://adijatinigam.gujarat.gov.in/home). - Click on the &quot;[APPLY FOR LOAN](https://adijatinigam.gujarat.gov.in/gtdcloan)&quot;.- Select the scheme name &quot;Foreign Study&quot;.\n- Fill the registration form: Full Name (as per Aadhaar Card), Gender, Date of Birth, Aadhaar Number, Mobile Number, Uder name, Password for login, Confirm Password.\n- Click on the &quot;Sign Up.\n- After successful registration, User ID and Password will be generated.\n\n##### ***Application Process***\n\n- Enter User ID, Password, and Captcha Code.\n\n\n- After login, schemes applicable to your caste will be displayed.\n- Click on the scheme you want to apply for.\n- Fill the &quot;Application Form&quot; and upload the required documents\n- Click Save Application. The system will generate an Application Number.\n- Click Print Application.\n\n<br>\n\n"
        }
